{"tid":1841992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[年初二超突發聲援] 1月26號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:02:53.000Z","uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40f1b5b2138fbc9815d42d09d9eecf03d1542aec","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">🛑緊急聲援🛑</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n聽 日（2 6 日 - 年初二）<br />\n早上九點半‼️<br />\n<br />\n🏛西 九 龍 裁 判 法 院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️羅德泉署理總裁判官<br />\n<br />\n#詳情未知<br />\n跪求大家支持手足🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"85e1263244b3d166c2b2c630ef3e871ab46ec65a","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2Facrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=1895d5fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"26e04ac62ecd93531a662bd106ba6ef1b6374f7f","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2Facrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e47133b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2Facrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=9505f8df\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"c3bb131e88b7b698b1f115723421146e75ee4b61","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvOeUaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvOeUaS.jpg&h=264db028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cde5745845e69e2cf5b707c4b30751980612f6b4","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n西九龍裁判法院交通<br />\n<strong>九龍西</strong><br />\n旺角彌敦道：118           [東京街西]<br />\n旺角亞皆老街：18, 701 [東京街西]<br />\n旺角亞皆老街：296C     [英華書院]<br />\n大角咀：12                     [東京街西]<br />\n大角咀：32                     [蔬菜統營處]<br />\n黃埔：12A                      [東京街西]<br />\n黃埔：30X                      [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍東</strong><br />\n土瓜灣：45                  [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n黃大仙：214                [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n九龍塘：702                [東京街西]<br />\n石硤尾：702                [東京街西]<br />\n秀茂坪：214                [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n九龍灣：296C             [英華書院]<br />\n觀塘：296C                 [英華書院]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n東區：118                   [東京街西]<br />\n南區：171                   [怡閣苑]<br />\n灣仔：905                   [怡閣苑]<br />\n灣仔：914                   [東京街西]<br />\n中西區：904, 905       [怡閣苑]<br />\n中西區：914               [東京街西]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界東</strong><br />\n北區：270B.                      [元州邨]<br />\n大埔：W3(青沙)&gt;286X    [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n沙田：280X(青沙)&gt;286X [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n大圍：286X.                      [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n馬鞍山：86C                     [東京街]<br />\n將軍澳(尚德)：296C        [英華書院]<br />\n將軍澳：98C                     [長沙灣遊樂場]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界西</strong><br />\n元朗：68X                        [元州邨]<br />\n天水圍：69X, 265B         [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(大興)：66X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(虎地)：67X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(新墟)：67X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(市中心)：60X         [元州邨]<br />\n屯門(良田)：58X             [元州邨]<br />\n屯門碼頭：59X                [元州邨]<br />\n深井：52X                        [元州邨]<br />\n荃灣：30X, 33A, 234X    [元州邨]<br />\n梨木樹：36A                   [東京街西]<br />\n海濱花園：238X             [元州邨]<br />\n石籬：32                          [麗蘿樓]<br />\n葵涌：33A, 37                 [元州邨]<br />\n葵涌：36A                       [東京街西]<br />\n青衣：41                          [元州邨]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"4bf71c8cdea72d10178911899af5988fec672219","tid":1841992,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"邊單case?"},{"pid":"16818ddb2bd364b4bb2344e773df14d6abba9420","tid":1841992,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf71c8cdea72d10178911899af5988fec672219","tid":1841992,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"邊單case?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>【屯門炸彈】四男女串謀製炸彈被捕 O記：企圖新年示威製造混亂</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/426074/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E8%A3%BD%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-o%E8%A8%98-%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%8